mixed *query_skills() 

Description
	Returns the currently set skills array on the living object.  This is
used by other commands and players to do any clever things they need to do
with the skills array.  Returns an array of the format 
({ name, exp, lvl, ({
       name2, epx, lvl ({ ... }),
   name3, exp, lvl ({ }) });
eg
({ "fighting", 0, 0, ({ }),
   "magic", 10000, 10, ({
          "spells", 1000, 11 ({ }),
          "points", 0, 10, ({ }),
          }),
   });
